data.title: Venkatesh Daggubati: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Venkatesh Daggubati: Check out the list of all Venkatesh Daggubati movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Venkatesh Daggubati news on Times of India.
data.text:
Venkatesh Daggubati and Anil Ravipudi's film titled 'Sankranthiki Vasthunnam'

etimes.in / Jul 12, 2024, 13:30 (IST)

'SVC 58', directed by Anil Ravipudi, starring Venkatesh Daggubati, Aishwarya Rajesh, and Meenakshi Chaudhary, began in Hyderabad. Muhurat pujah held; set for Sankranti 2024. Action drama with love triangle in crime story. Music by Bheems Ceciroleo, cinematography by Sameer Reddy, editing by Tammiraju. Third project after 'F2' and 'F3'; tentatively titled Sankranthiki Vasthunnam.

Arjun Rampal joins Rana, Venkatesh Daggubati in season 2 of 'Rana Naidu'

IANS / Jul 23, 2024, 18:19 (IST)

Actor Arjun Rampal, who was recently seen in the sports action film 'Crakk', has joined the cast of the Telugu-language streaming show 'Rana Naidu'.

Pawan Kalyan touches down in Mumbai for Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant’s Shubh Aashirwad ceremony - See photos

etimes.in / Jul 13, 2024, 19:43 (IST)

The Ambani family hosts a lavish Shubh Aashirwad function for Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant, with celebrities like Pawan Kalyan and Venkatesh Daggubati in attendance. The post-wedding celebration at Jio World Convention Centre attracts stars from Bollywood, business, and sports.

Director Atlee, Venkatesh Daggubati and other south celebs grace Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant's Shubh Aashirwad ceremony - See photos

etimes.in / Jul 13, 2024, 19:23 (IST)

The post-wedding celebrations of Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant are ongoing with the Shubh Aashirwad ceremony featuring notable guests from the South Indian film industry. The event is set to be a memorable affair, highlighting the strong connections between the Ambani family and celebrities.

Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant wedding: Ram Charan-Upasana Konidela, Rana Daggubati - Miheeka Bajaj grace the event in traditional extravaganza

etimes.in / Jul 12, 2024, 23:31 (IST)

Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant are getting married today at the Jio World Convention Centre in Mumbai. Several celebrities like Rajinikanth, Ram Charan, Rana Daggubati, and others have been spotted at the venue in traditional attire.

Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant's wedding : Atlee and his wife Priya join the 'Anant's Brigade', Venkatesh Daggubati makes stylish entry in traditional attire - WATCH

etimes.in / Jul 12, 2024, 19:04 (IST)

At the Jio World Convention Center, BKC, Mumbai, Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant's wedding saw Atlee Kumar and Priya in matching outfits with 'Anant’s Brigade' print on Priya's blouse. Venkatesh Daggubati attended in ethnic wear. Celebrities including Rajinikanth, Sanjay Dutt, Janhvi Kapoor, Sara Ali Khan, and Ananya Pandey graced the star-studded event.

Aishwarya Rajesh joins the cast of Anil Ravipudi's directorial, starring Venkatesh Daggubati

etimes.in / Jul 03, 2024, 12:33 (IST)

Venkatesh Daggubati and director Anil Ravipudi reunite for the third time with Aishwarya Rajesh in their upcoming film 'SVC 58'. The actress portrays a powerful character, as seen in the poster. Fans anticipate another successful collaboration between the talented trio, building on their previous hits 'Nash' and 'F2: Fun and Frustration'.

Venkatesh Daggubati and Varun Tej Konidela to reunite for Anil Ravipudi's 'Fun and Frustration' franchise: Report

etimes.in / Jun 11, 2024, 21:55 (IST)

Venkatesh Daggubati and Varun Tej Konidela reunite for 'Fun and Frustration' sequel directed by Anil Ravipudi and produced by Dil Raju. They starred in 'F2: Fun and Frustration' and their recent movies were 'Saindhav' and 'Operation Valentine' based on real events.

When I'm in Hyderabad, I crave for home-cooked food: Raja Kumari

May 06, 2024, 14:08 (IST)

Hyderabad Times caught up with the Telugu ammayi, rapper Raja Kumari, in Hyderabad and she couldn’t stop gushing about her love for the City of Pearls. She also spoke about her Telugu roots, friendship with Ram Charan, Allu Arjun and shared about working interesting with Rana Daggubati.

Victory Venkatesh Daggubati's daughter Hayavahini ties the knot with Nishanth

etimes.in / Mar 16, 2024, 10:18 (IST)

Victory Venkatesh Daggubati's second daughter, Hayavahini, recently exchanged vows with Nishanth in a lavish ceremony at Ramanaidu Studios, attended by luminaries from the Telugu film industry and politics. The festivities, filled with love and joy, marked the beginning of a new journey for the newlyweds surrounded by family and close friends.

Venkatesh Daggubati shares a cryptic note on happiness!

etimes.in / Mar 19, 2024, 14:35 (IST)

Venkatesh Daggubatitakes to social media to share cryptic post on struggles and happiness. Fans suspect actor is sad over continuous flops. The actor on work front was last seen in 'Saindhav'.

Venkatesh Daggubati begins his next project with director Anil Ravipudi

etimes.in / Apr 11, 2024, 17:18 (IST)

Venkatesh Daggubati and Anil Ravipudi team up for a crime thriller, unveiling a story of an Ex-Cop entangled in a web with ex-girlfriends and a wife. The movie, set for Sankranti 2025, promises suspense and a triangular love story.

Salman Khan reveals about Ram Charan's surprise cameo in Salman Khan's 'Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan'

Feb 23, 2024, 17:47 (IST)

Ram Charan gained popularity after the superhit 'RRR'. He made a guest appearance in Salman Khan's film 'Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan' and shared the screen with Salman Khan and Venkatesh Daggubati. Currently, he is wrapping up the shooting schedule of 'Game Changer', a political drama, and there is no official announcement about the release.

Nawazzudin Siddique says he regrets making his Tamil debut with Rajinikanth's 'Petta'

etimes.in / Feb 19, 2024, 14:01 (IST)

Nawazuddin Siddiqui feels guilty about his Kollywood debut in 'Petta'. He charged more for a role he didn't understand, fooling everyone. He took lessons before his Telugu debut in 'Saindhav', where he did his own dubbing.

Venkatesh Daggubati's 'Saindhav' gears up for its OTT release!

etimes.in / Jan 25, 2024, 11:43 (IST)

The Telugu film 'Saindhav' starring Venkatesh Daggubati is set for its digital premiere on Amazon Prime on February 9. The action thriller, directed by Sailesh Kolanu, grossed Rs 15 crore at the box office. The film was initially said to be out on the digital platform in March, but it was released on the OTT platform on the 28th day after its release date in theaters.

'Saindhav' preview: The Venkatesh Daggubati starrer promises cinematic wonders!

etimes.in / Jan 12, 2024, 19:24 (IST)

Vekatesh Daggubati's next Saindhav is all set to release in theatres tomorrow. Directed by Sailesh Kolanu, the movie features Venkatesh Daggubati Baby Sara, Shraddha Srinath, Andrea Jeremiah, Arya. The music for the film is composed by Santhosh Naryanan. The film's runtime is 138 minutes and the movie has been certified U/A. The film is releasing in theatres on January 13, 2024 and it is indirectly clashing at the box office with Naa Saami Ranga, Guntur Kaaram and Hanu Man.

In pictures: Venkatesh Daggubati visits Kanakadurga temple in Vijayawada

etimes.in / Dec 12, 2023, 15:13 (IST)

Venkatesh Daggubati gears up for the release of his film 'Saindhav'. The movie will release on January 13, 2024. The promotions are in full swing, with the actor visiting the Kanakadurga temple in Vijayawada. Along with the cast and crew, a special pujah was performed to seek blessings. The pictures of Venkatesh Daggubati, Shraddha Srinath, Balanati, and director Sailesh Kolanu are going viral on social media. Venkatesh also visited the Babai Hotel after his temple visit.

'Saindhav' box office collection day 3: Venkatesh Daggubati starrer to touch Rs 10 crore in India

etimes.in / Jan 16, 2024, 02:20 (IST)

Venkatesh Daggubati's 75th film, 'Saindhav,' earned an estimated Rs 6.65 crore in its first two days at the Indian box office. On day three, it garnered around Rs 3.15 crore with a 41.02% Telugu occupancy. Directed by Dr. Sailesh Kolanu, the action thriller features Venkatesh as a devoted father confronting his mysterious criminal past to secure funds for his daughter's medical treatment. Nawazuddin Siddiqui makes his Telugu debut as the main antagonist.

Venkatesh Daggubati's humble gesture steals hearts at 'Saindhav' press meet

etimes.in / Jan 13, 2024, 10:30 (IST)

The pre-release buzz surrounding the film reached a crescendo during the promotional events, but it was Venkatesh's small yet impactful gesture that became the highlight. . Venkatesh Daggubati won over the crowd at a Saindhav movie press meet with his act of humility, rejecting the allure of a grandiose chair. His request for a regular chair showcased his preference for equality and resonated with the audience, earning him widespread appreciation.
